sdp/verification/t-002@20260416t043834z-verify.md:56:One minor gap: the audio roughness metric uses spectral-diff (first-difference magnitude), while the tracker roughness uses psychoacoustic dissonance intervals. Both are valid proxies but differ in semantics. This divergence is not documented. Not blocking.
